Durban - We are thrilled to announced that Taxify, the international transportation network company, have partnered with us to ensure care-free and safe trips to and from our awesome new home, Sibaya Casino and Entertainment Kingdom, for our visitors.

 Offering all new Taxify riders R80 off their first-round trip and their loyal clients R50 off a round trip, you can now relax and enjoy the 40 th edition of the Mercury Wine Week knowing that your trip is sorted and that you and your friends are safe.

 


 To redeem your Taxify promo code for Mercury Wine Week 2018 as a first-time rider of Taxify, simply follow the steps below: Step 1: Download the Taxify app: Android or Apple. Step 2: Add your card as a payment method on the app.  Step 3: Select promotions and enter the promo code MERWEEK2018 for new users and MWW2018 for current users Step 4: Request a trip!

See you there!

 


Important information:  1. T&C apply: Codes offer a value percentage off only.  2. Codes will only be active from August 29-31, 2018

